    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The goal isn't to replace running or gym workouts. It's to replace sitting.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The goal isn't to replace running or gym workouts. It's to replace sitting.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "icon": null,
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "id": "dac519a9-c7ff-4749-a3f2-f1d17c50d404",
    "parent": {
      "type": "page_id",
      "page_id": "333deabd-9164-80ec-b2cb-dba2c59c15cb"
    },
    "created_time": "2026-03-30T12:05:00.000Z",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-30T12:05:00.000Z",
    "created_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "last_edited_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I have a suspicion that the body doesn't care whether you walked 10km in one go or spread it across eight hours of gentle walking. What it cares about is that you moved. That blood flowed. That muscles engaged. That you weren't stationary for the majority of your waking hours.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I have a suspicion that the body doesn't care whether you walked 10km in one go or spread it across eight hours of gentle walking. What it cares about is that you moved. That blood flowed. That muscles engaged. That you weren't stationary for the majority of your waking hours.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "icon": null,
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "id": "c0c35446-666e-4dae-b45c-b1befe2dd201",
    "parent": {
      "type": "page_id",
      "page_id": "333deabd-9164-80ec-b2cb-dba2c59c15cb"
    },
    "created_time": "2026-03-30T12:05:00.000Z",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-30T12:05:00.000Z",
    "created_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "last_edited_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The research on prolonged sitting is grim. The research on NEAT (non-exercise activity thermogenesis) — the calories you burn through daily movement that isn't formal exercise — is encouraging. Walking at 3 km/h while working is pure NEAT.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The research on prolonged sitting is grim. The research on NEAT (non-exercise activity thermogenesis) — the calories you burn through daily movement that isn't formal exercise — is encouraging. Walking at 3 km/h while working is pure NEAT.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "icon": null,
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "id": "2efcfa11-6d7e-4927-b4e4-03b5fa800f19",
    "parent": {
      "type": "page_id",
      "page_id": "333deabd-9164-80ec-b2cb-dba2c59c15cb"
    },
    "created_time": "2026-03-30T12:05:00.000Z",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-03-30T12:07:00.000Z",
    "created_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "last_edited_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The real test: I'm going to enter a long trail race later this year. Not to compete, but to see if walking for several km a day at a desk translates into any kind of endurance base. My theory is that it will. The body adapts to what you do most, and if what I do most is walk, I should be able to walk a very long way.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The real test: I'm going to enter a long trail race later this year. Not to compete, but to see if walking for several km a day at a desk translates into any kind of endurance base. My theory is that it will. The body adapts to what you do most, and if what I do most is walk, I should be able to walk a very long way.",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "icon": null,
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
  },
